#
# turris_greylist
#
# ipv4 hash:ip ipset
#
# [Turris Greylist] (https://www.turris.cz/en/greylist) IPs 
# that are blocked on the firewalls of Turris routers. The 
# data is processed and clasified every week and behaviour of 
# IP addresses that accessed a larger number of Turris 
# routers is evaluated. The result is a list of addresses 
# that have tried to obtain information about services on the 
# router or tried to gain access to them. We do not recommend 
# to use these data as a list of addresses that should be 
# blocked but it can be used for example in analysis of the 
# traffic in other networks.
#
# Maintainer      : Turris
# Maintainer URL  : https://www.turris.cz/en/greylist
